(firstQuint)CHARITE vs.

 ALIF 5-Year Follow-up.

 This study is an extension out to 5 year follow-up of a randomized comparative IDE trial of the CHARITE cent Artificial Disc vs.

 ALIF with the BAK cage for treatment of degenerative disc disease.

 The original 2-year trial demonstrated non-inferiority of the CHARITE cent compared to ALIF.

 This extension will continue to follow-up the original outcome measures and will also examine adjacent segment progression.

